WEBVTT

00:05:57.414 --> 00:06:02.826
Later, he'd even go on to help develop
the epidural, for delivering mothers.

00:06:02.850 --> 00:06:04.985
But before he could focus on obstetrics,

00:06:05.009 --> 00:06:07.765
Bonica had to report for basic training.

00:06:10.373 --> 00:06:11.967
Right around D-Day,

00:06:11.991 --> 00:06:15.213
Bonica showed up
to Madigan Army Medical Center,

00:06:15.237 --> 00:06:16.387
near Tacoma.

00:06:16.783 --> 00:06:21.476
At 7,700 beds, it was one of the largest
army hospitals in America.

00:06:22.242 --> 00:06:24.936
Bonica was in charge
of all pain control there.

00:06:25.618 --> 00:06:27.618
He was only 27.

